laboratory_examinations.findings: Positive, showing a high concentration of specific IgE for latex (90.2 KU/l)
+ +++ reaction to cypress SPT observed 3 min after prick test execution, with subsequent diffused urticaria, dysphonia, dyspnoea, and itching hands.
